in this terraform project we are following the below
1) add the key pair to the instance
  a) first the key pair first we have to create a ssh key using ssh-keygen -t rsa
  b) after the ssh key is created copy the id_rsa.pub key to your working directory
2) create the instance
3) create a security group and add it to the instance
4) add userdata to the instance(addy.sh file)
